{
  "stem": "13524.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, now, don't go into town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't go out, because Elsner will get you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Were you wearing armbands, at that point?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- yes, we did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was no problem, because I often used to take the armband, put in the pocket, and-- and run without it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Rarely did I have the armband, outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And very shortly after, we were ushered into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for me, it was almost a relief.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now I felt more secure that Elsner won't get me, in-- in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But even in ghetto, I used to go out and go to that railway station to buy food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a policeman on the inside of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Polish policeman-- and a soldier on the outside of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And part of it was a brick wall, and part of it was wires-- what's that-- bar-- barbed wire-- in places-- that we should not escape, should not cross.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was also a tram going through the ghetto, out of the ghetto, into the Polish sector, and back into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the other end of the ghetto was leaving and going into city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for me, that was a marvelous way-- while they had to stop for the gate to be open for the tram-- to hop on on the tram and get out of the ghetto, equally back, to hop onto the tram and get back into the ghetto, with whatever I managed to buy.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was one particular conductor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His name was Stefan Grabowski.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was extremely nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He would specially open that door, or leave little ajar, so I could push it off, get in-- in that moment where the German policeman was past.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
